          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Preventing Regulatory Penalties for PPP Lenders Act </b></p> <p>This bill prohibits federal banking agencies from including Paycheck Protection Program loans as assets when calculating capital ratios, deposit insurance premiums, and other asset thresholds for certain small financial institutions. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2020-10-23T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
